                                                                                                 •   Ability to pull information from a variety of sources (different type of components,
                                                                                                     different operating systems, different platforms, etc.);
                                                                                                 •   Use of standardized specifications such as Extensible Markup Language (XML) and
                                                                                                     SCAP;
                                                                                                 •   Integration with other products such as help desk, inventory management, and incident
                                                                                                     response solutions;
